title: Secretary 2002 (x265 HEVC)
description:
Video........H.265
Audio........5.1ch AAC, 2.1ch AAC (commentary)
Subs.........English/Spanish
Container....MKV
Source.......Bluray

1st audio track is 5.1ch, 2nd audio track is the commentary track. For the subtitles, there were 2 English ones available. As far as I can tell, they are identical but I included them both anyways.

Ripped from DVD with MakeMKV, processed through Handbrake on High Profile.

File plays perfectly in Plex and VLC
